title: Neff x Deadmau5 Introduce Neffmau5
description: Neff Headwear, a leading active lifestyle brand, today announces its official partnership with world famous EDM artist deadmau5. The Neffmau5 collection includes co-branded tees, hats and hoodies. The signature line marks a creative collaboration between two of the most influential forces in their respective industries.
